@startuml Sequence Diagram - Application Startup
skinparam backgroundColor #FFE5F1
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceParticipant {
    backgroundColor #FFF0F8
    borderColor #9C27B0
}

title Sequence Diagram - Application Startup (Launcher Pattern)

== Server Startup ==
participant "JVM" as JVM
participant "Launcher\n(Server)" as ServerLauncher
participant "TCPServer" as TCPServer
participant "SModel" as ServerModel
participant "SView" as ServerView
participant "ServerSocket" as ServerSocket

JVM -> ServerLauncher : java -jar tcp_socket_server.jar\n(Launcher.main())
activate ServerLauncher
ServerLauncher -> TCPServer : TCPServer.main(args)
activate TCPServer
TCPServer -> TCPServer : launch(args)\n(JavaFX Application)
TCPServer -> ServerView : start(Stage)
activate ServerView
ServerView -> ServerModel : new SModel()
activate ServerModel
ServerModel -> ServerSocket : new ServerSocket(port)
activate ServerSocket
ServerModel -> ServerModel : load server.properties
ServerModel -> ServerSocket : bind to port 3000
ServerModel -> ServerSocket : listen for connections
deactivate ServerLauncher

note right of ServerLauncher
  **Launcher Class:**
  - JAR entry point
  - Delegates to TCPServer.main()
  - Required for JavaFX 21\nmodule system compatibility
end note

== Client Startup ==
participant "JVM" as JVM2
participant "Launcher\n(Client)" as ClientLauncher
participant "TCPClient" as TCPClient
participant "CView" as ClientView
participant "CModel" as ClientModel

JVM2 -> ClientLauncher : java -jar tcp_socket_client.jar\nlocalhost 3000\n(Launcher.main())
activate ClientLauncher
ClientLauncher -> TCPClient : TCPClient.main(args)
activate TCPClient
TCPClient -> TCPClient : parse args (IP, Port)
TCPClient -> TCPClient : launch(args)\n(JavaFX Application)
TCPClient -> ClientView : start(Stage)
activate ClientView
ClientView -> ClientModel : new CModel()
activate ClientModel
ClientView -> ClientView : show UI
deactivate ClientLauncher

note right of ClientLauncher
  **Launcher Class:**
  - JAR entry point
  - Delegates to TCPClient.main()
  - Required for JavaFX 21\nmodule system compatibility
end note

@enduml
